{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_40","type":"agent_message","text":"I have the scenario pinned down: capture an initial realtime cursor before writing starts, pause mid-segment so a durable partial draft exists, hydrate and replay chunk deltas from that saved cursor, then resume and verify the next session load sees the carried-forward text and resumed job position before finishing the remaining segments. I’m patching the backend test file and adding a short doc that explains this coverage."}}
