{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_59","type":"agent_message","text":"The first targeted run exposed a real hydration replay bug, not just a test issue: when recent composition progress events are replayed, `merge_composition_job_view()` drops `accepted_story_so_far`, so a resumed session can lose the latest manuscript text even though it exists in durable job metadata. I’m fixing that merge path now and then I’ll rerun the scenario plus broader composition-related checks."}}
